events.name: エントランスへの移動場所
エントランスへの移動場所
エントランスへの移動場所

parameters:
King Rex: I apologize for the strict security measures, but
I believe that now is the most dangerous time.
Clea: I think it's a natural decision.

King Rex: It seems that some nobles intend to support the
second prince. Both the second prince and General Atu have
disappeared from the palace...

King Rex: The details of continuing to cooperate with the
security will be discussed by the guild leader.

King Rex: Now, onto the main topic. I believe that all of
you are the greatest contributors.

King Rex: Caron cornered the dragon and defeated it, saving
many citizens of the empire. She is truly deserving of being
called a hero.
Clea: That's too kind of you to say.

King Rex: Although Caron has been given the title of Dragon
Slayer, we will revoke it and give her a new title from us.

King Rex: Due to the unprecedented achievements that deserve
titles for others as well, we will hold a separate ceremony
to confer them at a later date.
Clea: It is an honor beyond what I deserve, King Rex.

King Rex: I apologize for repeating myself, but your
achievements are unprecedented, so I want to repay you in
advance for what I can do.

King Rex: While I cannot grant any wish... I want to do my
best to fulfill your hopes as much as possible.

Mage Relm: Then, may I share? In this journey, I lost my
dream and gained a new one.

Mage Relm: That is to become an Archmage of the Magic
Academy.

Thief Nora: I want to make the Emma Mercenary Corps bigger!
I want to help people in need and those who have nowhere to
go.
Thief Nora: Also, I want to repay the people who helped me!

Priestess Sophia: I carry many sins, but from now on, I will
confront them and walk the path of a priestess.

Priestess Sophia: Under the guidance of Sister Eleo, my
mentor.

King Rex: Everything is difficult, especially when it comes
to interfering with the Magic Academy, even for a king--

Clea: King Rex, this is a declaration of determination. It's
not something I want someone else to fulfill, but something
I will fulfill myself.

Clea: We have learned that for us, hopes are something we
must seize with our own hands.

Clea: While I am deeply grateful for your offer, I
respectfully decline.

King Rex: I apologize for saying something insensitive.
That's why you are the heroes who defeated the dragon.
King Rex: ...May I hear another hope?

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: I... am a weak human.
That's why I want to work for the sake of those who are also
weak.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: Thank you for your
consideration, Lord Rex.

Young Rex: Thank you for telling me. With this, I can become
a king without hesitation, Alicia-san.

King Rex: Originally, this would be a banquet, but we hold
it when awarding achievements.

King Rex: Finally, let me express my gratitude once again. I
will not let your sacrifice be in vain.
King Rex: I promise to become that kind of king.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: エントランスへの移動場所

parameters:
Queen Caron: Your names, who have successfully defeated the
dragon, will be forever spoken of alongside the empire.

Queen Caron: I shall remember your names as well. Thank you
for saving the empire that my late husband loved.
Clea: That's too kind of you to say.

Queen Caron: I have heard that Clea was the central figure
in this heroic achievement. I shall bestow upon her the
honorary title for accomplishing such a great feat.

Queen Caron: Dragon Slayer... The title bestowed upon the
heroes who saved the nation. It is a title that has been
given to only a few individuals in the long history of the
empire.
Clea: It is an honor beyond what I deserve.
Queen Caron: Hehehe, you don't seem too happy, do you?

Queen Caron: In addition to the honorary title... I shall do
my best to grant your wishes as much as possible.

Queen Caron: Clea, do you have any wishes that you desire
from me?

Clea (My wish... it's something that even the most powerful
ruler cannot grant...)
Clea (... Neither my father nor my mother will come back)

Clea: It is an honor beyond what I deserve. I do not wish
for anything more than the honorary title.

Queen Caron: Hmm, then how about this? Let's build a
monument to commemorate your great achievement.

Queen Caron: And also... I heard that your ancestral home
was destroyed by a dragon.

Queen Caron: Let's give you a new home. Your late father and
mother would surely be pleased.
Clea: I think both my father and mother would be pleased.
Queen Caron: Do the others have any reservations?

Mage Relm: Queen Caron-sama! Please allow me to possess a
part of the dragon's remains!
Thief Nora: Ah, ah, please count me in too!
Queen Caron: Understood, I shall grant that wish.

Mage Relm: Um, if possible... I would like to request the
removal of the magic that turned me into an Archmage!

Queen Caron: As the queen, even I, a special existence,
cannot interfere with punishments in the academy.

Sister Eleo: I want to build a tavern in the village of
Irini, but I am being opposed by Lord Pido, a member of the
Senate nobility...
Queen Caron: Understood, I will talk to Pido about it.

Queen Caron: The protagonist of today's banquet, which will
be held later, is the Dragon Slayer.
Queen Caron: Enjoy to your heart's content.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.

Fotizona Guardsman: It is our duty to protect the beautiful
queen of the empire.

Fotizona Guard: You are not allowed to enter beyond this
point.

Fotizona Guard: You are not allowed to enter beyond this
point.
Queen Caron: Thank you for coming, General Atu.

Queen Caron: The shield of the empire, the eldest brother of
the imperial army... and the guardian of the royal family.

General Atu: I came here in response to your sudden summons,
but unlike you, I am a busy man.

General Atu: The disappearance of the magician, the
subjugation of the Camps thieves... It's as if someone from
somewhere has orchestrated this busyness.

Queen Caron: After the death of my husband... the empire is
standing on a very precarious balance.

Queen Caron: The guarantor of this balance is Senator Pilia
of the Senate and the greatest general in the history of the
empire standing before us.

Queen Caron: I have heard that there are forces trying to
dismantle what we have protected together.

Queen Caron: I believe in your unwavering loyalty, for the
sake of the royal family... above all, for the sake of the
Fotizona Empire.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
General Atu: You, what do you think you're doing!?

Queen Caron: Don't make a fuss. This is a decision to
protect the Fotizona Empire.

Queen Caron: If we can manage and mass-produce, we can
easily conquer neighboring countries like Tarasa overnight,
right?

General Atu: The Fotizona royal family has created a dragon,
the symbol of demons, of all things...!

Queen Caron: You, who was easily stabbed to death, should
understand the terrifying blood that flows in the royal
family.

Queen Caron: Even though I had noticed the danger and
imprisoned Lex, to release him into the wild and awaken the
blood of the royal family...

Queen Caron: Don't worry, General. This dragon here hasn't
fully awakened yet.

Queen Caron: That's just the strongest General Atu of the
Insurance Empire burying Lex and the others...

Queen Caron: I don't want to see the entire empire being
devastated by a dragon.

Queen Caron: Hehehe, I'm counting on you, the shield of the
empire, the eldest brother of the imperial army, the
guardian of the royal family... Atu.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.
Fotizona Guardsman: Please be respectful to Lady Caron.

Queen Caron: I have understood the outcome of the meeting
with General Atu and Agonia. You have worked hard.

General Atu: The noble members who were aligned with the
queen did not clearly state their position and remained
silent.

General Atu: It seems that the noble Casaro is moving. Not
only the nobles, but even the Senate has started to take
action!

Queen Caron: Oh my, it is truly terrifying. We must rely on
the brave general before us even more.

General Atu: Don't play dumb! That monster, the dragon, has
been completed, right?!

General Atu: If I have misunderstood... then explain that
confidence!

Queen Caron: The dragon is just a precaution... The one we
can rely on is General Atu, the guardian of the royal
family.

Queen Caron: Both I, who do not want Rex to become king, and
the general, do we not share the same sentiment?

General Atu: Do you intend to trample upon the traditions of
the empire and become a queen?!

Queen Caron: What are you talking about... I am just
fulfilling my role as the queen.

General Atu: Many people have defected from you due to the
movements of the Adventurer's Guild.

General Atu: The trust they have built up is what led to
this! Even if you become queen, the only thing you can build
is a fragile sand castle that will crumble!

General Atu: Because no one trusts you. Those who refuse to
believe will not be trusted by anyone!
General Atu: The conversation ends here.

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: I apologize for the wait. There
are no issues with controlling the grimoire or the dragon.

Queen Caron: Emoni, what do you think will happen at the
royal palace from now on?

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Are we not going to confront
Prince Rex...?
Queen Caron: Once you taste it... you'll want another one.

Queen Caron: It's a song that my mother used to often hum...
Yes, it's exactly right, it makes you want it.

Queen Caron: Dragons require corpses, and the more high-
quality ones, the better.

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Caron-sama... Could it be!? Not
only the Prince's faction, but General Atu and the soldiers
too...!

Queen Caron: You are a reliable person, unlike those who
cannot be used like a puppet, isn't that right?

Queen Caron: Let us witness the sight of fools being
trampled upon by overwhelming power together.

Queen Caron: I'm counting on you. From now on, you will be
in charge of the secret agency.
Queen Caron: Are you ready then?

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: U-Um, if I may... I don't know
when the royal palace will become a battlefield...

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: So... if you could please
restrain yourself at least for the time being--

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: ...Huh! Ah, please wait as I
guide you!

Queen Caron: I don't mind eliminating Emoni this time... but
is she a woman who has any use despite being useless?

Queen Caron: Just a little more, just a little more and it
will reach.

Queen Caron: My hand will reach the pinnacle I have longed
for...

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: ...H-here it is! We have

Queen Caron: Now, let me teach you the joy of your final

part of the dragon as [material].

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: W-When did I go wrong...? Was
it when I rebelled against my father and ran away from
home...?

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Or was it when I joined the
Adventurer's Guild...?

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: No, I know it well... It was

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Ugh... It's already too late...
I can't... turn back from here anymore...
